  <original-body>action_controller/templates/rescues/layout.erb is not xhtml compatible, that means that the error tracebacks are difficult to read on sites which are served with a content type of application/xhtml+xml to browsers like Firefox.

The fix is simple.  Change line one in the file from

  &lt;html&gt;

To

  &lt;html xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;&gt;

No other changes are required.</original-body>
